snippet.title: Stellar Blade - EVE Vignette | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Meet EVE, member of the 7th Airborne Squad, sent to Earth from an off-world Colony to save mankind from the malevolent Naytibas.

Reclaim Earth for Humankind in Stellar Blade, launching April 26, 2024 only on PS5.
Pre-order now for in-game bonuses.

#ps5games #ps5 #StellarBlade
